$ in the regimes\nwhen either $\\varepsilon=O(1)$ or $0<\\varepsilon\\le \\tau$. Numerical results\nare reported to confirm the error bounds and demonstrate the efficiency and\naccuracy of the MTI-FP method for the KG equation, especially in the\nnonrelativistic limit regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2014 04:47:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 May 2014 08:42:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-14"}
