ermination of these bounds and of the\nassociated reflection and transmission coefficients for actual plates with\ntilted perforations but also yields single expressions covering all usual cases\nof perforations: straight or tilted with a circular or an elliptical\ncross-section.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2014 14:44:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
