erties could suggest some hints on\nthe use of moist entropy (or ${\\theta}_{s}$) in cloud modelling or in mixing\nprocesses, with the marine Stratocumulus considered as a paradigm of moist\nturbulence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jan 2014 14:49:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2014 08:06:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2014 19:29:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2014 09:12:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-27"}
